---
title: Chorizo & Chickpea Shakshuka with Parmesan & Toasted Sourdough | Serves 2
description: Spice up your brunch time with this bold and flavourful shakshuka! Smokey chorizo, hearty chickpeas, and perfectly
poached eggs simmer in a rich, spiced tomato sauce—made for scooping with crusty sourdough.
